  description: The Halo franchise is a first-person shooter game that follows the
    protagonist (Master Chief) fighting against any faction that threatens all life
    in space. Initially, Master Chief is written as a typical stoic and traditionally
    masculine character. However, some criticise that in recent entries, he has become
    more emotionally dependent and vulnerable with his female AI companion.
